<committee-appointment-paragraph><header>Committee on Foreign Affairs:</header><text>Mr. Mfume (to rank immediately after Mr. Amo). </text></committee-appointment-paragraph> <committee-appointment-paragraph><header>Committee on Transportation and Infrastructure:</header><text>Mr. Deluzio.</text></committee-appointment-paragraph>

